Package com.crs.entity

Class Car

java.lang.Object
com.crs.entity.Car
public class Car extends Object
The Car class represents a vehicle in a car rental system. It encapsulates information about a car, including its identification, make, model, manufacturing year, daily rental rate, status, passenger capacity, and engine capacity.
